  "metadata": {
    "name": "Ensure the Logon Failure Delay is Set Correctly in login.defs",
    "description": "To ensure the logon failure delay controlled by <tt>{{{ login_defs_path }}}</tt> is set properly,\nadd or correct the <tt>FAIL_DELAY</tt> setting in <tt>{{{ login_defs_path }}}</tt> to read as follows:\n<pre>FAIL_DELAY {{{ xccdf_value(\"var_accounts_fail_delay\") }}}</pre>",
    "rationale": "Increasing the time between a failed authentication attempt and re-prompting to\nenter credentials helps to slow a single-threaded brute force attack.",
